{"tid":1810914,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"tvb今次仆街 張兆輝武漢返黎仲要唔撚帶口罩","createTime":"2020-01-04T09:06:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T09:46:33.000Z","uid":92376,"like":24,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"83d0e54834d80f4d931e97562fd3ea5f9c198f35","tid":1810914,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T09:06:25.000Z","msg":"死廢中唔知傳染病有潛伏期？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢回港　張兆輝唔使隔離：我OK喎！<br />\n<br />\n藝人張兆輝為無綫新劇《黃金有罪》出席記者會，因張兆輝剛從懷疑爆發不明肺炎的武漢回港，而記者會上都有不少工作人員都戴上口罩以保安全。問到張兆輝是需要和他保持距離？他笑言：「應該唔使啦，我ok喎！如果真係有事，自己會感覺到唔舒服嘅。」問到返港回家，家人可有特別措施應付？他謂：「佢哋都唔知有咁嘅事，其實我上去時都唔知嘅，你知我都飛嚟飛去，我尋晚返，今日就嚟記者會。」更提議記者：「你哋驚可以戴口罩。」<br />\n<br />\n政府快啲隔離電視城<br />\n我唔想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"172f7fce8b527c206171a3d3b3d16cdbb745999b","tid":1810914,"uid":225130,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T09:06:50.000Z","msg":"應該唔使啦，我ok喎！如果真係有事，自己會感覺到唔舒服嘅。"},{"pid":"a6666075087814c6cc376293925e5c5595ad10b8","tid":1810914,"uid":92376,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T09:07:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200104/photo/bkn-20200104152049223-0104_00862_001_01p.jpg?20200104161212\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200104%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200104152049223-0104_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20200104161212&h=04dfe586&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n戇撚鳩"},{"pid":"b73ae06c67611748827f2cbd8b5ad0c33935924b","tid":1810914,"uid":92376,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"172f7fce8b527c206171a3d3b3d16cdbb745999b","tid":1810914,"uid":225130,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"ci